<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
        <title>Acknowledgement of Form CRS</title>

        <link rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="180x180" href="img/favicon/apple-touch-icon.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="img/favicon/favicon-32x32.png">
        <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="img/favicon-16x16.png">

      <style>
        body {
            font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
        }
      </style>
    </head>
    <body style="background:#121212; padding:0; margin:0">
        The user, <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %>, has acknowledged they've
        received and reviewed the Prometheus Financial Advisors LLC Form ADV
        Part 2A and the Prometheus Financial LLC Brokerage Form CRS
        Relationship Summary. The user was provided a direct link to each of
        these forms (on the firm's publicly available  website) at the time of
        the user's acknowledgement. *We are also capturing their name, email
        and day/time they acknowledged the form CRS/Form ADV 2a.*

        <ul>
            <li>Name: <%= firstName %> <%= lastName %></li>
            <li>Email: <%= email %></li>
            <li>User ID: <%= id %></li>
            <li>Date: <%= date %></li>
        </ul>
    </body>
</html>
